version: 0.3.0
date-released: 2026-07-21
license: MIT
abstract: >-
  Daneshyar is a bilingual, open-source educational content engine that turns
  user-supplied university PDF books into grounded question answering,
  summaries, quizzes, flashcards, concept maps, and presentation drafts.
  The public beta combines a static GitHub Pages frontend with a FastAPI and
  Docker backend deployed on Render, supports Persian and English OCR, and can
  operate with local extractive fallbacks or optional OpenAI-based generation.
keywords:
  - artificial intelligence
